{"tid":21601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港光復戰爭紀念幣","createTime":"2016-12-04T03:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T03:33:41.000Z","uid":51388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb4b611372ca288c17374bdd85291955490f6fd","tid":21601,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"最近加拿大出左一個香港戰爭紀念幣，我覺得幾靚，所以同巴絲分享。香港一向被人忽略，邊會有人出戰爭紀念幣，戰爭戰勝日都係班東江縱隊出來抽水，仲點會有人知道加拿大士兵為香港犧牲，特此紀念加拿大犧牲同香港光復。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/110207_30b85e2377a4993f17444b0025dbdcb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F110207_30b85e2377a4993f17444b0025dbdcb0.jpg&h=add69f04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/110209_4a9c6601360dad1a106d4010446d9a9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F110209_4a9c6601360dad1a106d4010446d9a9e.jpg&h=f7bb0c87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/110211_267990290e8ac1c6804ad7138b7f9a1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F110211_267990290e8ac1c6804ad7138b7f9a1c.jpg&h=5ff32b29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/110212_13e042cb4de67e0f7b08824ed3083350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F110212_13e042cb4de67e0f7b08824ed3083350.jpg&h=77464d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/86Y6M81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F86Y6M81.jpg&h=bc6a8053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做工比較精細<br />\n利申，得一個"},{"pid":"00e5226b9e8c0286f035151fb2c55811ce1ddfa0","tid":21601,"uid":1051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:32:33.000Z","msg":"好靚"},{"pid":"583c8b5a4d512e8d01c52c9535756594d7676857","t